OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FAn app that blocks out social media
OL,8,Fthat has been trialled in several
OL,9,Fschools in England has been credited
OL,10,Fwith improving pupils' behaviour.
OL,12,FIn an impact assessment by the app's
OL,13,Fcreators, Blackout Education, the app
OL,14,Fwas shown to have led to positive
OL,15,Fimpacts on young people's focus and
OL,16,Foverall digital well-being.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
