OL,7,FThe Blackout app works by only
OL,8,Fallowing certain other apps to
OL,9,Ffunction on a smartphone. By
OL,10,Fdownloading the app on a device, it is
OL,11,Fable to block out other platforms that
OL,12,Fcan be distracting to learning, like
OL,13,Fsocial media.
OL,15,FThe creators say use of the Blackout
OL,16,Fapp is as close as UK schools can get
OL,17,Fto the recent under-16s social media
OL,18,Fban in Australia, meaning young people
OL,19,Fkeep their phones, but are blocked
OL,20,Ffrom certain apps that many fear are
OL,21,Fharmful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
