OL,7,FMark Hadley, Co-Founder and CEO of
OL,8,FBlackout Technologies, said: "We are
OL,9,Fnow seeing very promising indicative
OL,10,Fdata from this initial sample of more
OL,11,Fthan 5000 students at a range of
OL,12,Fschool types.
OL,14,F"As the national debate around young
OL,15,Fpeople, smartphones, and social media
OL,16,Fcontinues to rage here in the UK and
OL,17,Facross the world, we think that the
OL,18,Fresearch we are gathering will be a
OL,19,Fvaluable evidence-based contribution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
