OL,7,F"The ultimate measure for many parents
OL,8,Fwill be if the benefits also translate
OL,9,Finto improved grades and outcomes, and
OL,10,Fwe will be continuing to dig deeper
OL,11,Finto the data we are continuing to
OL,12,Fgather to establish that."
OL,14,FLast April, ITV News filmed at Glyn
OL,15,FSchool in Epsom, Surrey, which is one
OL,16,Fof the schools that has been trying
OL,17,Fout the app.
