OL,7,FAt the time, teachers and pupils at
OL,8,Fthe school spoke of the benefits of
OL,9,Fphones being effectively locked down
OL,10,Fduring school hours.
OL,12,FThe Blackout app has also been in use
OL,13,Fat the nearby Rosebery School, but one
OL,14,Fpupil there in Year 8 told me that
OL,15,Fsome children will uninstall the app
OL,16,Fand still find ways to access certain
OL,17,Fapps on their phones during the school
OL,18,Fday.
