OL,7,FThe same 12-year-old, however, also
OL,8,Fsaid she is glad that the Blackout app
OL,9,Fmainly prevents other students from
OL,10,Fbeing able to take - and share -
OL,11,Funwanted photos of each other, or
OL,12,F"mugs" as they're often called.
OL,14,FBlackout's early impact assessment
OL,15,Freport, released on Thursday, draws on
OL,16,Fdashboard analytics, safeguarding
OL,17,Flogs, behavioural records, school
OL,18,Fvisits and direct pupil feedback,
OL,19,Ftaken from a sample of more than 5000
OL,20,Fstudents in England in Years 7-11.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
