OL,7,FA member of teaching staff at one
OL,8,Funnamed school said: "It doesn't
OL,9,Fdemonise mobile phones.
OL,11,F"We all need mobile phones in the
OL,12,Fmodern world, so therefore having a
OL,13,Fsolution that teaches and educates us
OL,14,Fon how to use those mobile phones
OL,15,Fresponsibly, correlates very well with
OL,16,Four overall digital strategy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
