OL,7,FAnother teacher at a different school
OL,8,Ftold researchers: "I don't want there
OL,9,Fto be the temptation of phone use
OL,10,Fduring the day and I think better
OL,11,Ffriendships will be made if others are
OL,12,Fnot distracted by phones.
OL,14,F"In addition, it reduces the risk of
OL,15,Fchildren being covertly on their
OL,16,Fphones during lessons, which
OL,17,Fultimately will impact on the whole
OL,18,Fclass's learning experience."
