OL,7,FITV News was told that some parents
OL,8,Fare worried about privacy when
OL,9,Fdownloading the app on their
OL,10,Fchildren's devices, while others
OL,11,Fprefer to set up their own parental
OL,12,Fcontrols to control their children's
OL,13,Fscreen time and app use themselves.
OL,15,FThe blackout app is one of several
OL,16,Fmeasures schools have been looking at
OL,17,Fto address the issue of smartphones in
OL,18,Fschools, with nearly all having rules
OL,19,Fof some form in place to curb their
OL,20,Fuse.
