OL,7,FCampaigners like Esther Ghey are
OL,8,Fcalling on the government to go
OL,9,Ffurther to implement a statutory ban
OL,10,Fon their use in schools.
OL,12,FShe has recently said that a ban would
OL,13,Fhave helped her daughter, Brianna, who
OL,14,Fshe has described as "addicted" to her
OL,15,Fphone. The 16-year-old was killed by
OL,16,Ftwo teenagers in February 2023.
OL,18,FBrianna's former school in Warrington
OL,19,Fhas now adopted the use of Yondr
OL,20,Fpouches, which effectively lock
OL,21,Fsmartphones away for the day.
